                <note rend="inline" type="source">875.00/122: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Albania</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grant-Smith</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-05-20T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20, 1924—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>31. Your 43, May 18 and 44, May 19, 3 p.m. Department has informed Navy of
                    substance of your telegrams and in accordance with your recommendation has
                    expressed desire that the Commander of United States Naval Forces in European
                    waters be authorized to despatch a destroyer to Durazzo upon receipt of a
                    request to that effect from you or the Embassy at Rome. Embassy at Rome has been
                    advised in the premises by telegraph.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
